---
---
<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-brand">
      <span class="footer-logo">🎮</span>
      <span class="footer-title">CHILEONLINE STUDIOS</span>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-credits">
      <p class="credit-line">Desarrollado con <span class="heart">♥</span> y sarcasmo desde Chile</p>
      <p class="credit-sub">v2026.7.1 — Todos los derechos reservados (como los impuestos)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <span class="footer-link">Términos de Servicio</span>
      <span class="footer-separator">·</span>
      <span class="footer-link">Política de Privacidad</span>
      <span class="footer-separator">·</span>
      <span class="footer-link">Reportar Bug (al gobierno)</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-header);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .footer-inner {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .footer-brand {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .footer-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .credit-line {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .heart {
    color: var(--red);
  }

  .credit-sub {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .footer-link {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .footer-link:hover {
    color: var(--cyan);
  }

  .footer-separator {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
  }
</style>
